Class GalleryPhotographBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • gallery.beans.AbstractBean<GalleryPhotograph>
      • gallery.beans.GalleryPhotographBean

  • @Path(value="/galleryphotographs")
public class GalleryPhotographBean
extends AbstractBean<GalleryPhotograph>
    GalleryPhotograph Enterprise Java Bean, maps to a GalleryPhotograph Hibernate Entity. Also a REST service mapping to /YourPersonalPhotographOrganiser/resources/galleryphotographs.
